410
00:20:43,120 --> 00:20:44,585
for, you know,

411
00:20:46,120 --> 00:20:47,267
a proper send-off.

412
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:50,580
Quick session of congress.

413
00:20:51,520 --> 00:20:53,110
Sink the Bismarck, if you will.

414
00:20:53,800 --> 00:20:55,789
And by the way, did I mention

415
00:20:57,120 --> 00:21:00,110
it is a matter of national security.

416
00:21:04,000 --> 00:21:05,101
Mmm.

417
00:21:09,280 --> 00:21:11,860
It's very difficult for me
as well, you know,

418
00:21:11,960 --> 00:21:13,789
this thing that's come between us.

419
00:21:14,440 --> 00:21:16,304
I know, darling.

420
00:21:22,120 --> 00:21:24,540
- Mmm.
- No, no. Steady yourself.

421
00:21:24,640 --> 00:21:26,310
